{"tid":1185001,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【六四30】教聯會：學生爬軍車掟物屠殺解放軍","createTime":"2019-06-04T03:56:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T04:33:10.000Z","uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4ca701627a7c542a59de25ff65153b42e58af220","tid":1185001,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T03:56:56.000Z","msg":"【六四30】教聯會否認屠城 親中團體：學生爬軍車掟物屠殺解放軍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年是六四30周年，港台節目《城市論壇》今日討論。支聯會秘書李卓人表示，中共30年來鎮壓民主自由，「每一日喺中國同香港發生緊，香港今日有政治犯，係邊個搞出嚟？」他提到，香港於八九民運時，大家不分背景，一同譴責中共鎮壓，「教聯會都有上街支持中國民主化」，呼籲市民出席今年六四集會，珍惜香港僅存可悼念六四的空間及自由，以燭光悼念及控訴，傳承當年為民主的精神及感情。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">教聯會會長黃均瑜認為，中共政府30年前處理六四事件是犯錯，「解放北平不需要開一槍一炮，點解建國30幾年後要動用槍炮？」但他指岀不會支持支聯會，批評其於平反六四上加入對中央政府不滿等其他訴求，不再只是悼念。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mtd1hOv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmtd1hOv.png&h=02dd8648&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190602/59668641\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190602%2F59668641&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9Cgq3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=bddbc52d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190602%2F59668641&h=e41bd76d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190602/59668641</a>"},{"pid":"037633fa7551da49690c2f8bb285e86a0a77cc08","tid":1185001,"uid":66390,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T03:58:05.000Z","msg":"點撚解咁都講得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />為撚左名利...<br />\n2014過多幾年比人形容為學生用催淚彈掉警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5786cf3e029d34ab8a4e0420f1f9efa8d839910","tid":1185001,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T04:00:41.000Z","msg":"空手打贏坦克？<br />\n條友係咪痴左線"},{"pid":"9d9fabea8811e2fe7270dd7f3ea75ac305ade97e","tid":1185001,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T04:01:51.000Z","msg":"葉問上身都打唔過坦克車啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"b59e81c92c9fd8dbe0a699f0cc88bb7d68339c43","tid":1185001,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T04:02:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xxbY4u8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxxbY4u8.png&h=5b7c437a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n洋蔥圈：「<span style=\"color: red;\">我當時一方面感到震驚，因為一直以來對嗰場學生運動，都感覺到係相當和平嘅一場運動，我覺得冇咁嘅需要。亦都感覺到有啲迷惑李鵬總理喺學生已經宣佈咗話要停止絕食、撤出天安門嘅時候，仲有一個咁樣嘅決定。<br />\n<br />\n中國政府喺事前作嘅承諾，後來都一一落空，包括不秋後算賬，包括軍隊唔係用來對付學生呢啲承諾，後來都落空咗。香港嘅未來同中國政府畀香港嘅承諾，無論係中英聯合聲明裏面嘅承諾、基本法裏面嘅承諾，係有好密切嘅關係，如果中國政府係咁唔重視自己嘅承諾嘅話，係好難怪香港人對中國政府失咗信心嘅。</span> 」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190523/20685000\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190523%2F20685000&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9Cgq3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=617b34d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190523%2F20685000&h=485a7e4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190523/20685000</a>"},{"pid":"5f5de531f4ae5ff201bb89fb5f8623ae78195be7","tid":1185001,"uid":76020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T04:03:03.000Z","msg":"全部東方不敗黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a34b4cd39e5dc4560b763579ab8da73f856e3da8","tid":1185001,"uid":33099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T04:05:00.000Z","msg":"如果係咁 即係中共企係道德高地 點解一直唔公開資料 唔俾人討論？"},{"pid":"388756c2ab0eb3847bd607ba5ff14c112435edbf","tid":1185001,"uid":44309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T04:05:29.000Z","msg":"有槍，有炮，有坦克嘅解手軍畀平民學生屠殺到，解手軍都廢吓。"},{